Commentary Text: Shami to Klaasen, out Caught by Miller!! Miller dropped one earlier but he ain't dropping this one. End of yet another terrific knock from Heinrich Klaasen. Seam-up full delivery from Shami, was there to be hit but Klaasen didn't get the desired connection on it. Commentary Text: Mohit Sharma to Sanvir Singh, out Caught by Sai Sudharsan!! Mohit Sharma strikes first ball! With mid-off inside the circle, Sanvir Singh walks down the track to try and elevate it over him. However, it was a short ball from Mohit that got big on the batter. Sanvir Singh swung his bat only to get a top-edge. Sai Sudharsan moves to his right from third man, keeps his eyes on the ball and calmly catches. SRH have now lost half their side. Commentary Text: Shami to Anmolpreet Singh, out Caught by Rashid Khan!! Poor from Anmolpreet Singh! 134.7kph, length ball that seams away a bit outside off. The length wasn't short enough to be pulling/heaving. Anmolpreet Singh plays across the line and the ball balloons up off the top-edge. Rashid Khan runs in from third man to gobble it up. The Tewatia drop isn't costly. Anmolpreet Singh c Rashid Khan b Shami 5(4) [4s-1]
